		REST Item Unit Name
	</h1>

	<p>Creates, updates, deletes or lists unit names.<br />Units are used to specify the content of a variation. Units are created based on the International System of Units (ISO) and then linked to variations. The unit name is displayed in the online store. As such, unit names must be saved for all languages in which items are offered for sale.<br />Units can be managed using the route <b>/rest/items/units</b>.</p>

